title: [Darkstone, Dungeon]
description: Sticky cobwebs cling to your face, despite your best efforts to brush them away.  The webbing is tougher and stickier than any you've ever encountered before.  A small pot set high on a wall sheds a flickering light over the area, just enough to turn the webs into shadowy traps.
